  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Lighton Duo is a Challenging Puzzle Game.<br><br>The goal in each level is to assemble the circuit and turn on all the lights. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/88f7746652a3adb5a134837d4c3d0715.poster.avif?t=1688079467\" width=504 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/88f7746652a3adb5a134837d4c3d0715.webm?t=1688079467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/88f7746652a3adb5a134837d4c3d0715.mp4?t=1688079467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/bef94e6a2edda62abc4adb118b11ab51.poster.avif?t=1688079467\" width=490 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/bef94e6a2edda62abc4adb118b11ab51.webm?t=1688079467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/bef94e6a2edda62abc4adb118b11ab51.mp4?t=1688079467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50 hand-crafted levels;<br></li><li> Choose any level to play;<br></li><li> A fun puzzle game (even for those who have no knowledge of electronic circuits);<br></li><li> Made for Sokoban style lovers;<br></li><li> At some levels, it is possible to assemble the circuit in more than one way;<br></li><li> If you make a short circuit on battery, it will explode. (Be careful).</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Lighton Duo is a Challenging Puzzle Game.<br><br>The goal in each level is to assemble the circuit and turn on all the lights. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/88f7746652a3adb5a134837d4c3d0715.poster.avif?t=1688079467\" width=504 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/88f7746652a3adb5a134837d4c3d0715.webm?t=1688079467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/88f7746652a3adb5a134837d4c3d0715.mp4?t=1688079467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/bef94e6a2edda62abc4adb118b11ab51.poster.avif?t=1688079467\" width=490 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/bef94e6a2edda62abc4adb118b11ab51.webm?t=1688079467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566250/extras/bef94e6a2edda62abc4adb118b11ab51.mp4?t=1688079467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50 hand-crafted levels;<br></li><li> Choose any level to play;<br></li><li> A fun puzzle game (even for those who have no knowledge of electronic circuits);<br></li><li> Made for Sokoban style lovers;<br></li><li> At some levels, it is possible to assemble the circuit in more than one way;<br></li><li> If you make a short circuit on battery, it will explode. (Be careful).</li></ul>",
